reviewText: This was purchased as a Christmas gift for our family. I love the convience of them all being in the one case. We did have an issue with the 2nd disc skipping in our vehicle's player but otherwise, very pleased with everything.

It was nice to have all 3 of these movies in one set. I really enjoyed Home alone part 1 and 2 as a child and now my kids can have them and watch them whenever they want. The only reason I gave 4 stars rather than 5 is because I don't enjoy part 3 as much as the first 2 movies because of the different kid they use in part 3 and because I didn't think it was as funny as the first 2.

If you are American and don't know about this movie, here is your chance. This is what we watch on Christmas day. Hilarious! This movie deals with some of the mistakes we make as parents and what we will do for our children in great comic fashion. It also shows how independent we should teach our children to be, you never know what could happen.
